    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out! It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
